### Programs Exploited (Game Themes)

- **Feeding Our Future** - Fake meal distribution during COVID (largest case)
- **CCAP** - Child Care Assistance Program (phantom children, empty daycares)
- **EIDBI** - Autism therapy services (fake diagnoses, inflated billing)
- **Medicaid/PCA** - Personal Care Attendant fraud (nonexistent services)
- **Housing Stabilization** - Fraudulent billing for housing assistance

